headline: Assessing Aflac’s Value After Recent Digital Expansion and Price Swings
summary: Wondering if Aflac could be a hidden value in today's market? You're not alone, and now is a great time to put its price tag under the microscope. While Aflac's stock has climbed 1.1% in just the last week and is up an impressive 8.0% year-to-date, there has been some volatility, with the share price actually down 1.0% over the last year.
